refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
mixedpg_select resourceconnection stringtable_name arrayassoc_array intoptionsPGSQL_DML_EXEC
pg_select 根据 assoc_array 数组中的 field=>value 值来选择记录。成功的查询返回和 assoc_array 指定的条件相匹配的包括记录和字段的数组。
如果指定了 options，pg_convert 会按照指定选项作用于 assoc_array 之上。 &warn.experimental.func;

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 &return.success;  Returns string if PGSQL_DML_STRING is passed
 via options.

  &reftitle.examples;



    pg_select example


<?php 
  $db = pg_connect('dbname=foo');
  // This is safe, since $_POST is converted automatically
  $rec = pg_select($db, 'post_log', $_POST);
  if ($rec) {
      echo "Records selected\n";
      var_dump($rec);
  } else {
      echo "User must have sent wrong inputs\n";
  }
?>
